d recall than a term based approach in identifying definitions that contain complex patterns and occur across sentence boundaries full pdf version available here view the phenologue project back to search results information last updated wed oct 5 2011 make corrections to this publication go stanford biomedical infomatics only all of stanford school of medicine contact information maps & information site map stanford university
